show.description: When the president of Stewart Group mysteriously dies at home, his daughter Florence is left blind and determined to uncover the truth. Suspecting her father's protector, Walt, of being the culprit, she embarks on an investigation that unravels hidden secrets—and leads her to unexpected love.
